### ==========================================
### 资源模块 API 测试
### ==========================================

### 0. 获取 Token
# @name login
POST http://localhost:18081/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "admin",
  "password": "XiyuAdmin2026!"
}

@token = {{login.response.body.data.token}}

### 1. 正常流程：BAR 资产列表
GET http://localhost:18081/api/resources/bar-assets?page=0&size=10
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 2. 正常流程：创建 BAR 资产
POST http://localhost:18081/api/resources/bar-assets
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "API测试资产-{{$randomInt 1 9999}}",
  "type": "FACILITY",
  "value": 50000,
  "status": "AVAILABLE",
  "acquireDate": "2026-01-01",
  "remark": "API测试创建"
}

### 3. 正常流程：费用台账列表
GET http://localhost:18081/api/resources/expenses?page=0&size=10
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 4. 正常流程：创建费用记录
POST http://localhost:18081/api/resources/expenses
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "projectId": 1,
  "category": "TRANSPORTATION",
  "amount": 1888.88,
  "date": "2026-05-01",
  "expenseType": "差旅费",
  "description": "API测试费用"
}

### 5. 正常流程：BAR 借用记录列表
GET http://localhost:18081/api/resources/bar-assets/1/borrow-records
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 6. 正常流程：借用 BAR 资产
POST http://localhost:18081/api/resources/bar-assets/1/borrow
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "purpose": "API测试借用"
}

### 7. 边界：借用不存在资产
POST http://localhost:18081/api/resources/bar-assets/999999/borrow
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "purpose": "测试"
}

### 8. 正常流程：归还 BAR 资产
POST http://localhost:18081/api/resources/bar-assets/1/return
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 9. 边界：未借用就归还
POST http://localhost:18081/api/resources/bar-assets/2/return
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 10. 正常流程：合同借用列表
GET http://localhost:18081/api/resources/contracts/borrows?page=0&size=10
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
